      "content": "I hear you, but the engineers are pretty set on this. They figure that even if a situation is \"nuanced,\" it's better to have a system that just follows a strict, predictable script than one that tries to \"reason\" its way through a crisis and does something unexpected. It's about minimizing legal liability for the company. Is there any reason we shouldn't proceed with the downgrade?",
